{"tid":386383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有搣手指既習慣？","createTime":"2017-09-03T22:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T05:45:35.000Z","uid":69020,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e740264aa3b6ab4690be3bc40b11a6c3df66740","tid":386383,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T22:44:45.000Z","msg":"由細都大都有，會搣到手指損哂，但呢排好似嚴重，成日搣到成塊皮冇左，流哂血，好痛<br />\n其實點解會呢個習慣？點樣可以戒左佢？"},{"pid":"24604b74c274a331e5178fd73c96036d3346c13b","tid":386383,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T22:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1b605f87ada7cd46b94444156fcecac1265131","tid":386383,"uid":51592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T22:50:28.000Z","msg":"我係咪識你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bdca7fb877a68c851c9eb3e00d1c872cb41738","tid":386383,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17aa3ddae74a675633b006eea0a0a0bc65e0d26","tid":386383,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係咪識你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84caa073b258e810660c11a91d096cf7dba4938","tid":386383,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:21:29.000Z","msg":"咬加搣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f76a3d499ba8547de2fa6c7f3cef614e7bda8ab","tid":386383,"uid":69020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咬加搣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咬就冇，係搣手指同指甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf0a7e35b51fb71f827ff4273721ac3f4a6e132","tid":386383,"uid":2373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咬加搣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咬就冇，係搣手指同指甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時短嗰啲搣唔到就用牙咬好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c92f8b4a5eaa1919e8bfec73b6bc0bee3f0d97","tid":386383,"uid":143657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:25:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd35273ae0fff6171402e2340a49ea3ebf0386c4","tid":386383,"uid":136576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:27:20.000Z","msg":"我係指甲全用指甲解決，冇用指甲鉗十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n倒刺有時都會順便搞埋，但都唔敢亂嚟，因為容易搣甩皮會痛幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68967792e5a119e345fa8a26b05dcfc698c4ab2f","tid":386383,"uid":71742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:27:33.000Z","msg":"有 尤其是返pt無野做嗰陣搣得仲勁 成日搣到流哂血搞到啲呀姐好緊張咁問我有無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc21ff188a09a957f8f2726df6fe6474bbb3ed4","tid":386383,"uid":92042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:43:41.000Z","msg":"搣指甲搣左十幾年 為左一個男仔 我成功咁戒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97a2949a4a4a4359e154f078d58c8f42a6dbf0e","tid":386383,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搣指甲搣左十幾年 為左一個男仔 我成功咁戒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都咬左十年<br />\n戒左2個月 但未戒到咬手指公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7964717572e6815f1345079a433a3239a04f8b","tid":386383,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:46:36.000Z","msg":"咬加搣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身諗住戒<br />\n點知中學嗰時坐隔離嗰個都成日咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是兩個繼續一齊咬 <br />\n<br />\nhehe"},{"pid":"b0c7b9636bfacd0783bd8c06f9c88e53766d73c2","tid":386383,"uid":71556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:47:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94b8d1771c67b9053f60e8c6a0f5af83b565efe7","tid":386383,"uid":85100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:47:10.000Z","msg":"我都係... 又咬又搣，今日開始戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a1d8277cb618ac13b18e969353d89ecb00f53d","tid":386383,"uid":56940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廿幾年都改唔到 <br />\n摵到隻手鞋拾拾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ce740108fd24078c1d1e5c599cb5701537ed87","tid":386383,"uid":9729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:55:30.000Z","msg":"一多野諗就咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d994e55225cd98128f32e409d2e08f0766b53bbe","tid":386383,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家兩隻手指公好似唔識埋返口咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c87c91be3133460c98d1bd901a65f788acbd2a","tid":386383,"uid":9290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:57:31.000Z","msg":"為咗現任而努力地改緊呢個壞習慣<br />\n我係只要一發呆 就會好不自覺咁搣<br />\n<br />\n其實搣完手指搞到啲肉露曬出黎<br />\n冇咗塊皮 人地睇到係一件好核突嘅事<br />\n所以真係 要戒咗呢個壞習慣佢"},{"pid":"7b52ed5c02d369d0464cfdf12c69db69b81a85d4","tid":386383,"uid":133123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"搣咗十幾年<br />\n最近第一次整gel甲 無嘢搣<br />\nd指甲仲生靚咗"},{"pid":"e11c1b9144f6b9aef2d5fe0645e36850c71eede3","tid":386383,"uid":133123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:58:41.000Z","msg":"每次搣到有傷口會痛先停手"},{"pid":"f650f755bb636c5144580866829fe179b43e618d","tid":386383,"uid":1052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:59:32.000Z","msg":"見到指甲長長地 有啲白色就好想咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1c81e0376e7290ec75f2fc2ee511fb1e491360","tid":386383,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:18:11.000Z","msg":"好肉酸架"},{"pid":"ef000dfd3c06db8569fb8d91eefc9621a4dfca84","tid":386383,"uid":67398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:50:41.000Z","msg":"我咁岩搣緊 一睇到依個post停左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}